Trade/Device Name(s): Quantimetrix Drug of Abuse Urine Screen Control
Instrument(s)/Platform(s): other drugs of abuse screening methods
Document Summary: FDA 510(k) summary for Quantimetrix Drug of Abuse Urine Screen Control for monitoring performance of urine drugs of abuse screening assays
Indications for Use Summary: Intended to monitor the performance of Abuscreen ONLINE, AxSYM, Triage, and other drugs of abuse screening methods for detecting drugs in unknown urine specimens
